speech: I am tall, colorful and the nicest flower. Ask me anything.
I'm blue, which is a rather rare color for a flower. Ask me something else.
I'm gray. Just one shade of gray. Ask me something else.
I played a part in a 1981 Bollywood movie. Ask me something else.
I love Bollywood movies. Ask me something else.
I'm red, but please don't judge me based just on that. Ask me something else.
